aa(lp116
VSo, all of these projects have a humanistic sense to them,
p117
aVand I think as designers we need to really think
p118
aVabout how we can create a different relationship
p119
aVbetween our work and the world,
p120
aVwhether it's for business,
p121
aVor, as I'm going to show, on some civic-type projects.
