p123
aVvalue to business, value to the users also,
p124
aVbut I think it's the values that we put into these projects
p125
aVthat ultimately create the greater value.
p126
aVAnd the values we bring
p127
aVcan be about environmental issues,
p128
aVabout sustainability, about lower power consumption.
p129
aVYou know, they can be about function and beauty;
p130
aVthey can be about business strategy.
p131
