aa(lp134
VSo Jawbone is a project that you're familiar with,
p135
aVand it has a humanistic technology.
p136
aVIt feels your skin. It rests on your skin,
p137
aVand it knows when it is you're talking.
p138
aVAnd by knowing when it is you're talking,
p139
aVit gets rid of the other noises that it knows about,
p140
aVwhich is the environmental noises.
p141
aa(lp142
VBut the other thing that is humanistic about Jawbone
p143
aVis that we really decided to take out all the techie stuff,
p144
aVand all the nerdy stuff out of it,
p145
aVand try to make it as beautiful as we can.
p146
aVI mean, think about it:
p147
aVthe care we take in selecting sunglasses, or jewelry,
p148
aVor accessories is really important,
p149
aVso if it isn't beautiful, it really doesn't belong on your face.
p150
aVAnd this is what we're pursuing here.
