aa(lp152
VBut how we work on Jawbone is really unique.
p153
aVI want to point at something here, on the left.
p154
aVThis is the board, this is one of the things that goes inside
p155
aVthat makes this technology work.
p156
aVBut this is the design process:
p157
aVthere's somebody changing the board,
p158
aVputting tracers on the board, changing the location of the ICs,
p159
aVas the designers on the other side are doing the work.
p160
